      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/17/47826599/10316b5178d5109d597f415d6e7903dc_3484001310435653319.png",
                "id": "talent23019",
                "key": "征涛",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "征涛"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>本角色附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">捉浪 · 涛拥之守</span>并<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备技能</span>：<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">踏潮</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/17/47826599/32f8641a1f41763d29139a4b8a6a4971_8728595940864657694.png",
                "id": "talent57502",
                "key": "捉浪",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "捉浪"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">雷兽之盾</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/17/47826599/0cce59adfbce4cdc1347ce3556a6f15c_8359848486425386355.png",
                "id": "talent63563",
                "key": "斫雷",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "斫雷"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着雷元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超载</span>：本伤害+2，目标强制切换到下一个角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超导</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感电</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下2次草元素或雷元素伤害+1的[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化领域</span>]</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/17/47826599/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_7616857796688140699.png",
                "id": "talent79979",
                "key": "雷元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">准备技能</span></strong></p><p>有些技能无法被直接使用，而是需要一定次数的行动轮来进行<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备</span>。轮到一位牌手行动时，如果该牌手的「出战角色」正在<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备</span>技能，则跳过该牌手的行动；如果技能已经完成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备</span>，角色将会在此时直接使用此技能。（此类需要<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备</span>的技能，无法触发「使用技能后」效果。）只有「出战角色」才能<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备</span>技能；如果正在<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备</span>技能的「出战角色」被切换到后台，技能的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备</span>就会被打断。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">捉浪 · 涛拥之守</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p>准备技能期间：提供2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">护盾</span>，保护所附属的角色。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">护盾</span></strong></p><p>此护盾所保护的角色受到伤害时，将会消耗护盾来抵消伤害。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">踏潮</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>(需准备1个行动轮)</p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">雷兽之盾</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方角色普通攻击后：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方角色受到至少为3的伤害时：</span>抵消其中1点伤害。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>：2</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">持续回合</span></strong></p><p>每回合结束阶段，<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>-1；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/17/47826599/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_5315952590254392999.png",
